\b D. Technical Stack Recommendation\par
\b0 Backend: Python (scikit-learn, XGBoost, Prophet for forecasting)\par
Real\f3\_\f0 time Processing: Apache Kafka or RabbitMQ\par
Caching: Redis for competitor price data\par
Database: PostgreSQL for historical data + TimescaleDB for time-series\par
APIs: FastAPI for internal microservices\par
\par
